 <title>Feds feed Families</title>
 <link>https://energy.gov/ea/articles/feds-feed-families</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div  property=&quot;content:encoded&quot; class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt; &lt;p&gt;Representatives of the Office of Enterprise Assessments delivered more than 1,600 pounds of non-perishable food to the Manna Food Center on September 2, 2014 as part of the 2014 Feds Feed Families campaign. Manna feeds about 3,300  needy families in Montgomery County.   Manna also provides food to 48 Montgomery County soup kitchens, food pantries, group homes, and emergency shelters.&lt;/p&gt;
